name: Admin Console Release 25.10.0
description: This release of the Admin Console brings you some improvements. See below for details on some of the more notable changes applied to the Admin Console.

ADDED.text: In the profile management section under the Admin Console, the Reset Password URL and Resend Email URL fields will automatically pick the recently used URL value.

IMPROVED.text: Formatting of support ticket description has been updated.
Deprecated Social Providers are removed from Admin Console UI.
